Simple compiled language, fast builds, good for servers and tools, less flexible than some languages

Common type sizes:

| Type | Size |
| --- | --- |
| bool | 1 byte |
| byte / uint8 / int8 | 1 byte |
| int16 / uint16 | 2 bytes |
| int32 / uint32 / rune | 4 bytes |
| int64 / uint64 | 8 bytes |
| int / uint / uintptr | 4 bytes on 32-bit systems, 8 bytes on 64-bit systems |
| float32 | 4 bytes |
| float64 | 8 bytes |
| complex64 | 8 bytes |
| complex128 | 16 bytes |
| string header | 16 bytes on 64-bit systems, plus string data |
| slice header | 24 bytes on 64-bit systems, plus backing array |
| pointer | 4 bytes on 32-bit systems, 8 bytes on 64-bit systems |
